hopobject.body: How much notice do you have to give? zyflamend bph I find the sudden ‘superiority’ of the Oracle team dubious to say the least.  Initially New Zealand swept Team USA under the rug.  Indeed the America’s Cup would have concluded after a very brief regatta.  Seemingly the stakes, especially the investments and potential financial rewards were too significant for the competition to be settled so rapidly.  So, miraculously, thanks to the brilliance of … Larry Ellison, Team USA … found another gear.  Sorry, but this entire thing doesn’t smell right any longer and I have ceased to follow the Cup.
